      "date": "Sat, 22 Jan 2022 10:15:00 +0000",
      "snippet": "Dear Study Group, This is a friendly reminder about our scheduled study session taking place tomorrow. Here are the details: **Date:** Sunday, January 23, 2022 **Time:** 3:00 PM - 5:00 PM **Location:**",
      "body": "Dear Study Group,\n\nThis is a friendly reminder about our scheduled study session taking place tomorrow. Here are the details:\n\n**Date:** Sunday, January 23, 2022  \n**Time:** 3:00 PM - 5:00 PM  \n**Location:** Library Study Room B-12  \n\nWe'll be focusing on reviewing chapters 4-6 of our textbook and going through the practice problems for the upcoming midterm exam. Please remember to bring your notes and any questions you may have.\n\nLooking forward to seeing everyone there! Let me know if you have any conflicts or if there's anything specific you'd like to cover during the session.\n\nBest regards,  \nJane Doe  \n"
