      "body": "Hi Study Group,\n\nI hope this email finds everyone well!\n\nAs discussed, I am sharing the notes from our recent study session on Saturday, January 29th. Please find the key points covered during the session below:\n\n1. We reviewed the core concepts from Chapter 5 of the textbook.\n2. Discussed the example problems on pages 112–115 in detail.\n3. Agreed to focus on preparing for the upcoming quiz covering Chapters 4–6.\n4. Decided on the next study session date: Thursday, February 3rd, at 3:00 PM in the university library, Room 204.\n\nIf there’s anything I missed, or if anyone has additional points to add, please feel free to reply to this email. Let’s also ensure that everyone has a chance to review the material discussed before our next meeting.\n\nLooking forward to hearing from you all!\n\nBest regards,  \nJane Doe\n"
    },
