      "snippet": "Hello Study Group, I hope this email finds you well! I wanted to share some new study material that I came across, which I believe could be very useful for our upcoming group discussions. These",
      "body": "Hello Study Group,\n\nI hope this email finds you well! I wanted to share some new study material that I came across, which I believe could be very useful for our upcoming group discussions. These resources cover the topics we had talked about during our last meeting, including recent advancements and case studies that align with our course objectives.\n\nPlease check out the attached files and let me know your thoughts. If you'd like, we can also discuss integrating these materials into our next group session on Monday.\n\nFeel free to reach out if you have any questions or if there's anything else you'd like to share with the group.\n\nLooking forward to hearing everyone's insights!\n\nBest regards,  \nJane Doe  \njane.doe@gmail.com\n"
    }
